# 🚀 AutoDS AI — Multi-Agent AI Data Scientist (SaaS)

> Upload a dataset → Get insights, models, and business decisions automatically

---

## 🧠 Overview

**AutoDS AI** is a production-style AI system that automates the entire data science workflow using **Multi-Agent AI + RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)**.

It simulates how real data teams work by combining:
- 📊 Data Analyst (EDA & insights)
- ⚙️ ML Engineer (model building & evaluation)
- 💼 Business Analyst (decision-making)

All powered by **LLMs + Machine Learning pipelines**.

---

## 🔥 Key Features

- 📁 Upload CSV dataset  
- 📊 Automated EDA & visualization  
- 🤖 Multi-Agent AI system  
- 💬 Chat with your dataset (RAG powered)  
- ⚙️ Auto ML model building & comparison  
- 📈 Feature importance & predictions  
- 🔐 User login & project management (SaaS)  
- ⬇️ Download trained model  

